            ))
        } -->
        <Project
            title="Pseudo-Code Compiler"
            imageUrl="/img/pcc_example.png"
            actions={[]}
            invertColumns={false}
        />
        <p>
            My FInal-Year Project was to develop a runtime environment for
            pseudocode, as defined in
            <a
                href="https://mitpress.mit.edu/9780262046305/introduction-to-algorithms/"
                >Introduction To Algorithms</a
            > by <em
                >Thomas H. Cormen, Charles E. Leiserson, Ronald L. Rivest</em
            > and
            <i>Clifford Stein</i>.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Tokenises, parses, transpiles pseudocode to executable Python
